01:00:12,999 --> 01:00:15,209
Apa? Woo Shik pingsan?

1182
01:00:16,269 --> 01:00:17,879
Tadi dia tidak apa-apa.

1183
01:00:18,039 --> 01:00:19,039
Apa?

1184
01:00:19,339 --> 01:00:20,979
Tadi Woo Shik bersamamu?

1185
01:00:23,510 --> 01:00:25,050
Aku belum tahu pasti.

1186
01:00:25,249 --> 01:00:26,479
Nanti kutelepon lagi.

1187
01:00:32,189 --> 01:00:33,189
Soo Yeon.

1188
01:00:33,890 --> 01:00:35,390
Ada apa? Ada masalah?

1189
01:00:37,760 --> 01:00:38,859
Soo Yeon, kamu mau ke mana?

1190
01:00:38,959 --> 01:00:40,729
Sutradara akan segera tiba.

1191
01:00:40,729 --> 01:00:41,830
Soo Yeon!

1192
01:00:41,830 --> 01:00:45,999
"UGD"

1193
01:00:49,640 --> 01:00:50,740
Kepalaku sakit.

1194
01:00:51,379 --> 01:00:53,709
Woo Shik, kamu merasa lebih baik?

1195
01:00:54,050 --> 01:00:55,149
Hei, Kak.

1196
01:00:56,249 --> 01:00:57,479
Di mana aku?

1197
01:00:59,149 --> 01:01:01,649
Menurutmu di mana? Ini rumah sakit.

1198
01:01:01,720 --> 01:01:02,749
Rumah Sakit?

1199
01:01:03,089 --> 01:01:04,089
Kenapa aku di sini?

1200
01:01:04,089 --> 01:01:06,160
Kamu pingsan di depan stasiun penyiaran Soo Yeon.

1201
01:01:06,660 --> 01:01:08,089
Kenapa kamu pergi ke sana?

1202
01:01:09,629 --> 01:01:12,060
Soo Yeon terlambat untuk rapat,

1203
01:01:12,060 --> 01:01:13,399
